            <title>訊飛輸入法崩了，官方迴應：端午節活動配置出現 Bug，升級新版本即可恢復</title>
            <description>&lt;div class=&quot;tougao-user&quot;&gt;感謝 IT 之家網友 &lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1865992&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;軟媒用户 1865992&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D375533&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;衝葱&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1642737&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Alphonisorca&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D831895&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;洗個痛快澡&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1561882&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;反反反覆覆復&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1133406&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;n_newen&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1671489&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;格式化大法&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D276951&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;雷震子&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1761474&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;凌子傲&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1802554&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;無名可取甚煩&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1387764&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;司馬不平&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1165946&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;村口李大爺&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1754465&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;木南冰室打雜&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1769432&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;境界隨想&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1937885&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Apllo&lt;/a&gt; 的線索投遞！&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;p data-vmark=&quot;4dac&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;s_tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.ithome.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;IT 之家&lt;/a&gt; 6 月 5 日消息，今日晚間，大量 IT 之家網友反饋稱訊飛輸入法出現故障，包括但不限於輸入框無法彈出、顯示斷網等。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;bd07&quot;&gt;訊飛輸入法官方迴應稱：訊飛輸入法在配置端午節運營活動過程中出現 Bug，導致部分用户出現客户端崩潰問題。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;d3b9&quot;&gt;對此，輸入法團隊正在對此進行全力搶修，6 月 5 日晚會發布新版本修復問題，新版本發佈後、升級版本可恢復使用。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot; data-vmark=&quot;46d3&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/6/b195a055-c864-44d1-a799-89ae6496fa6b.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto&quot; w=&quot;635&quot; h=&quot;171&quot; title=&quot;訊飛輸入法崩了，官方迴應：端午節活動配置出現 Bug，升級新版本即可恢復&quot; width=&quot;635&quot; height=&quot;171&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-vmark=&quot;26df&quot;&gt;截至 IT 之家發稿，目前訊飛輸入法仍顯示為三天前更新的 13.1.1 版本，如果有遇到此類 Bug 的用户可以等晚些時候下載更新。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ad-tips&quot;&gt;廣告聲明：文內含有的對外跳轉鏈接（包括不限於超鏈接、二維碼、口令等形式），用於傳遞更多信息，節省甄選時間，結果僅供參考，IT 之家所有文章均包含本聲明。&lt;/p&gt;
        </description>
